3;\">To be eligible for CDU\u2019s masters scholarships for international students, applicants must meet the following criteria:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">They must be applying to begin their studies in Semester 2, 2023.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">They must meet the university&#8217;s academic and English language requirements for their chosen course.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">They must have an overall score of at least 95% in their highest completed qualification.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">They must be international students who pay international student fees.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">They must not receive a scholarship from an Australian or foreign sponsoring agency.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1829\" src=\"https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/female-student-holding-european-flag-sitting-floor-1.jpg\" alt=\"masters scholarships for international students\" width=\"854\" height=\"570\" srcset=\"https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/female-student-holding-european-flag-sitting-floor-1.jpg 854w, https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/female-student-holding-european-flag-sitting-floor-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/abroadin.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/female-student-holding-european-flag-sitting-floor-1-768x513.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 854px) 100vw, 854px\" \/><\/p>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #333333;\">10. Universit\u00e9 Paris-Saclay International Master\u2019s Scholarships<\/span><\/h2>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">Study in France<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">Master\u2019s Degree<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><a style=\"color: #333333;\" href=\"https:\/\/www.universite-paris-saclay.fr\/en\/admission\/bourses-et-aides-financieres\/bourses-internationales-de-master\/international-masters\">Official Scholarship Website<\/a><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #333333;\">The Universit\u00e9 Paris-Saclay is offering IDEX scholarships to international students to encourage them to enroll in its Master&#8217;s programs, which are nationally-certified degrees taught by its member institutions.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #333333;\">The university aims to facilitate the attendance of highly-qualified international students, especially those interested in pursuing research up to the doctoral level.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #333333;\">Eligibility for the scholarship is based on specific criteria. To be admitted to a Master&#8217;s program at Universit\u00e9 Paris-Saclay, students must have been accepted by one of the following institutions:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">AgroParisTech,<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">CentraleSupelec,<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">ENS Paris-Saclay,<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">INSTN-CEA,<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">IOGS,<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">UEVE,<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">UPSaclay,<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">or UVSQ.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #333333;\">Only students who meet specific criteria are eligible to apply for these masters scholarships for international students:<\/span><\/p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">Newly arrived international students who are 30 years old or younger during the election year.<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">Students of foreign nationality who have lived in France for less than a year and are not currently enrolled in a certification program or training course,<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">International students who have been living in France for less than a year and are taking language classes (type FFL),<\/span><\/li>\n<li><span style=\"color: #333333;\">In addition, students who have previously lived in France as part of a mobility program during their studies but did not receive certification.<\/span><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><span style=\"color: #333333;\">Join the Abroadin newsletter for exclusive content, helpful tips, and exciting updates. Do not miss out \u2013 subscribe today!<\/span><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #333333;\">Resources:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><a style=\"color: #333333;\" href=\"https:\/\/www.rhodeshouse.ox.ac.uk\/scholarships\/the-rhodes-scholarship\/\">https:\/\/www.rhodeshouse.ox.ac.uk\/scholarships\/the-rhodes-scholarship\/<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><a style=\"color: #333333;\" href=\"https:\/\/www.utwente.nl\/en\/education\/scholarship-finder\/university-of-twente-scholarship\/\">https:\/\/www.utwente.nl\/en\/education\/scholarship-finder\/university-of-twente-scholarship\/<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><a style=\"color: #333333;\" href=\"https:\/\/studyinitaly.esteri.it\/en\/call-for-procedure\">https:\/\/studyinitaly.esteri.it\/en\/call-for-procedure<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><a style=\"color: #333333;\" href=\"https:\/\/www.daad.de\/deutschland\/stipendium\/datenbank\/en\/21148-scholarship-database\/?status=&amp;origin=&amp;subjectGrps=&amp;daad=&amp;q=public%20policy&amp;page=1&amp;detail=50026397\">https:\/\/www.daad.de\/deutschland\/stipendium\/datenbank\/en\/21148-scholarship-database\/?status=&amp;origin=&amp;subjectGrps=&amp;daad=&amp;q=public%20policy&amp;page=1&amp;detail=50026397<\/a><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #333333;\"><a style=\"color: #333333;\" href=\"http:\/\/www.ed.ac.uk\/schools-departments\/student-funding\/postgraduate\/international\/medicine-vet-medicine\/glenmore\">http:\/\/www.ed.ac.uk\/schools-departments\/student-funding\/postgrad